5,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"個人覺得冇計㗎喎, 自甘墮落<br />\n作埋啲垃圾Pop<br />\n唔係話Pop依個Genre垃圾<br />\n係佢地作埋作埋堆Pop歌真係難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新碟首先好膚淺咁睇啲歌長度已經知唔對路<br />\n全部得3分鐘多啲<br />\n有啲直情3分鐘都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當首歌好簡短咁得6 Part (Intro, Verse x2, Chrous x2, Outro)<br />\n每Part得30秒都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁話唔定編曲好聽呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry, 全部係Taka後面罰企啦<br />\n每首歌都好悶<br />\n感覺寫完分半鐘Intro, Verse, Chorus<br />\n之後Copy and Paste湊夠3分鐘一首歌咁<br />\n<br />\n有啲人話Live會好聽好多<br />\n我屌啦<br />\n依堆咁嘅罰企歌<br />\n唔通成個Tour都要陪Taka罰企咩<br />\n啲樂器聲出返當然會好返啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢地真係鍾意依類歌<br />\n定為咗迎合人地巿場先作依類歌<br />\n如果係後者真係會鄙視佢地<br />\n依家嘅OOR完全冇哂屬於自己嘅風格"},{"pid":"b3cf1e522ff165c4cb67248382247dfb8c0d8bd8","tid":1047683,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e047ae766cb009131cb125eaeda2cc5645896cb3","tid":1047683,"uid":15862,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5f50bd09b5ca889a26694cc19459480e56b3d7e5","tid":1047683,"uid":92947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"想聽佢地唱返舊歌都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追左五六年 <br />\n睇住佢地愈做愈大雖然都幾開心<br />\n但係好似慢慢無咗oor嘅影子<br />\n對社會嘅控訴、成長嘅不滿<br />\n甚至以前嗰團火都好似唔見咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢地創團既目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都向住個個方向行緊 點會冇火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"日本仔真係好撚勁"},{"pid":"8cf8dadf1fa171047ea687fb32517d8103ee6b11","tid":1047683,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img 