/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4a252eb8a4a2c131e49d5a1f312f65979a707686","tid":1047683,"uid":168901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"個人認為35xxxv個album最正"},{"pid":"1167117ba44972c48102c0af9e023f4ff6e2129d","tid":1047683,"uid":134687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c89a3093233b87c20bfe23c938848c8fca53b3c","tid":1047683,"uid":234751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ef1e474a419becfcb32f622013fe3d6de36ae72","tid":1047683,"uid":39369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53cb8f44059e8bb7a8198be9f5ef8fc0018dcbfd","tid":1047683,"uid":234751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"我都有睇過佢地既故事, 知道佢地既目標<br />\n但都真心覺得呢隻碟好幫唔落<br />\n之前聽歌聽完真心會覺得好有力量好有動力面對所有事, 呢隻碟冇<br />\n最多都係得wasted night<br />\n<br />\n但都會係死忠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"一失落個陣聽let's take it someday就會有番動力<br />\n新歌真係無feel&hellip;<br />\n佢地為左拎格林美而改到咁商業好似有d變左質咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"但完全唔覺得依加既風格有可能拎到GRAMMY<br />\n明明特色係好重要..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"agree 睇返grammy rock album 全部都係有特色既歌<br />\n雖然oor 而加個production 幾好，但係唔出眾"},{"pid":"00969388f0e6944233fe2f21e4d69b9d36e1e3da","tid":1047683,"uid":140835,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"個方向根本一早就錯哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比如,<br />\n我做飲食, 想打入日本巿場<br />\n咁我一定唔會揀日本菜整壽司<br />\n會揀返茶餐廳個類嘅香港特式食品啦<br />\n<br />\n係人都明嘅嘢, 係得佢地唔明<br />\n依家玩爛隊Band就想解散<br />\n垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab14c7ca14b7d24f0c606dc31bf33685e3cc15e3","tid":1047683,"uid":14850,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oxbHyqia6_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoxbHyqia6_4&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=a5f9849e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oxbHyqia6_4</a><br />\n早排睇到 非打手<br />\n<br />\n［頭盔］唔同意見咋，唔係引起鬧戰［頭盔］<br />\n咁我覺得佢地有佢地自由，冇必要限死同一style既，作為死忠我覺得尊重同欣賞佢地就得啦，觀點角度姐，唔鍾意聽咪由佢囉，聽其他band仔囉，（架仔鬼佬仲有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n無話佢地轉型唔好，我都好懷念以前punk &amp; rock既oor，但過去係過咗去，我到宜家都會成日聽佢地啲舊歌，我唔係oor，我唔知佢地係咪好想轉型定係玩厭punk rock/ 抑或想跟主流打入歐美（好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），咁但係佢地再係舊方面突破定係玩pop元素咁係佢地自由嚟既，支持就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（我見出面有啲人直頭踩到oor地底泥咁 何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n利申死忠"},{"pid":"3bbec5fe2fb5fe949ff21f94aaff6dc112f3265c","tid":1047683,"uid":207877,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00969388f0e6944233fe2f21e4d69b9d36e1e3da","tid":1047683,"uid":140835,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"個方向根本一早就錯哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比如,<br />\n我做飲食, 想打入日本巿場<br />\n咁我一定唔會揀日本菜整壽司<br />\n會揀返茶餐廳個類嘅香港特式食品啦<br />\n<br />\n係人都明嘅嘢, 係得佢地唔明<br />\n依家玩爛隊Band就想解散<br />\n垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"你又知而家佢地100％為咗市場作歌?<br />\n成十年唔通會玩死日本風格?<br />\ntaka自己都講過而家比較鍾意country嘢<br />\n佢個playlist都唔係淨係得搖滾啦<br />\n玩爛隊band都講得出口，人地寫歌嘅心血就比你咁撚樣侮辱"},{"pid":"ffeb5b9e0449f6dea3da8025e90d8c5dc633a28c","tid":1047683,"uid":207877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a290666e57996a9799a71a3ac192fdea6d993939","tid":1047683,"uid":140835,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"個人覺得冇計㗎喎, 自甘墮落<br />\n作埋啲垃圾Pop<br />\n唔係話Pop依個Genre垃圾<br />\n係佢地作埋作埋堆Pop歌真係難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新碟首先好膚淺咁睇啲歌長度已經知唔對路<br />\n全部得3分鐘多啲<br />\n有啲直情3分鐘都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當首歌好簡短咁得6 Part (Intro, Verse x2, Chrous x2, Outro)<br />\n每Part得30秒都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁話唔定編曲好聽呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry, 全部係Taka後面罰企啦<br />\n每首歌都好悶<br />\n感覺寫完分半鐘Intro, Verse, Chorus<br />\n之後Copy and Paste湊夠3分鐘一首歌咁<br />\n<br />\n有啲人話Live會好聽好多<br />\n我屌啦<br />\n依堆咁嘅罰企歌<br />\n唔通成個Tour都要陪Taka罰企咩<br />\n啲樂器聲出返當然會好返啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢地真係鍾意依類歌<br />\n定為咗迎合人地巿場先作依類歌<br />\n如果係後者真係會鄙視佢地<br />\n依家嘅OOR完全冇哂屬於自己嘅風格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"你唔啱聽啫 唔代表啲歌係垃圾"},{"pid":"8d9c43f6121a6eb468ec29c6023625cf0a99e2c8","tid":1047683,"uid":237198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T18:04:01.000Z","msg":"致所有話佢哋唔想再玩 隊band 或者 玩爛隊band  嘅人<br />\n你可以話佢哋依家啲歌好差，<br />\n但 我相信佢哋絕對仲有投入大部分心機喺隊band ，我唔認為無心仲會一年開99場100場show 而且全世界咁走嚟走去<br />\n你估全年咁 舟車勞動 好過癮咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：死忠，但認同 新專 麻麻"},{"pid":"44006eaac757aebe8fff98354e8d3301d3bc7360","tid":1047683,"uid":35648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89482e51eec79eca2983bacd245b11da957f8245","tid":1047683,"uid":222739,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4a1aca09e9a3c57ab898ac5252abff224754c476","tid":1047683,"uid":222739,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"佢地都係抄"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"sor自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢地風格係抄Ellegarden<br />\n可惜到2010散band"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"你都戇撚鳩，講幾句野可以幾乎每part都錯<br />\n1. 散你老味咩停止活動呀<br />\n2. 停都唔係2010停呀柒頭，2008呀<br />\n3. Ellegarden上年因為版稅問題復出開3場演唱會全部One Ok Rock都有份做嘉賓，你有無撚聽過抄歌者走去做original嘉賓呀？<br />\n<br />\n由你講少少facts都錯到七彩就知你根本唔撚熟Ellegarden走出嚟鳩up"},{"pid":"9fa2f22c2c682be79024467988330037e7554561","tid":1047683,"uid":4660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T19:53:28.000Z","msg":"仲記佢地第一次來香港我買到最前，同taka零距離個下感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經好鍾意，可惜依家真係唔啱口味，希望佢地可以完成到佢地既目標啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 明白無可能要求隊band keep住一個曲風太耐，但始終都係鍾意舊曲風<br />\n<br />\n利申keep it real開始loop，35xxxv開始少聽，ambitions淨係聽過we are，新碟連聽都無聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea24a218d6ac6bcf070be756ec32cc170e6cadb","tid":1047683,"uid":164373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d9c43f6121a6eb468ec29c6023625cf0a99e2c8","tid":1047683,"uid":237198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T18:04:01.000Z","msg":"致所有話佢哋唔想再玩 隊band 或者 玩爛隊band  嘅人<br />\n你可以話佢哋依家啲歌好差，<br />\n但 我相信佢哋絕對仲有投入大部分心機喺隊band ，我唔認為無心仲會一年開99場100場show 而且全世界咁走嚟走去<br />\n你估全年咁 舟車勞動 好過癮咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：死忠，但認同 新專 麻麻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:20:33.000Z","msg":"首先佢地一定唔係唔想再玩隊band<br />\n佢地既大方向亦都無變<br />\n但不得不承認今次呢隻碟係令人失望<br />\n佢地今次選擇既曲風明顯失去自己風格<br />\n大部分既歌轉頭就唔記得<br />\n連pop易上口呢個最大元素都做唔到<br />\n明顯就兩頭都唔到岸<br />\n只能夠希望呢隻碟佢地當吸取經驗<br />\n<br />\n記得當初首先聽到eye of the storm呢首既一小段<br />\n仲好期待隻碟<br />\n點知隻碟整體差外 連eye of the storm全首都只係比到人到喉唔到肺既感覺"},{"pid":"0010b960ad8a50c2c68f2b6efe2fb16dcf6183c2","tid":1047683,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e047ae766cb009131cb125eaeda2cc5645896cb3","tid":1047683,"uid":15862,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5f50bd09b5ca889a26694cc19459480e56b3d7e5","tid":1047683,"uid":92947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"想聽佢地唱返舊歌都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追左五六年 <br />\n睇住佢地愈做愈大雖然都幾開心<br />\n但係好似慢慢無咗oor嘅影子<br />\n對社會嘅控訴、成長嘅不滿<br />\n甚至以前嗰團火都好似唔見咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢地創團既目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都向住個個方向行緊 點會冇火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"講真，唔通30歲仲唱emo仲作內秘心書個類歌咩，人大個左會變"},{"pid":"4e4f273cdb80787a60ceb72370f04e6aecc30436","tid":1047683,"uid":12914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"好想現場聽一次violin version既karasu &amp; et cetrea<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba3832c600cbe1d1a9ad41ade9c1b489a91767b","tid":1047683,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cbd12ded2427bd8e85d99d596ddbb51c080afa2","tid":1047683,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45cf7b5e5cf90948b70b0402339eb32477118fe2","tid":1047683,"uid":68925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WABKz2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWABKz2Q.png&h=5bef2c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個fd send比我 補圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gqjapan.jp/culture/bma/20190319/one-ok-rock-taka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgqjapan.jp%2Fculture%2Fbma%2F20190319%2Fone-ok-rock-taka&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=260037bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://gqjapan.jp/culture/bma/20190319/one-ok-rock-taka</a><br />\n出處係呢本雜誌，今日網上公開咗上面果段嘅原文"},{"pid":"2ce07cdb851f6b9939d34ee7d8060b3de6fd4a2b","tid":1047683,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/10969taka/p/Bvtp-fNlFPq/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=2hz6a7b60zgx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagr