 /><br />\n巴打邊到見到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"應該係官網<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KjiQAv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KjiQAv.png&h=6b1b67cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}